<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 05:59:30 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Lenovo MWC 2022 新品巡禮　ThinkPad 首用 ARM 架構　抵玩入門白電競筆電</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/08/lenovo-mwc-2022-intro/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=lenovo-mwc-2022-intro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 08 Mar 2022 05:59:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[gaming]]></category><category><![CDATA[Ideapad]]></category><category><![CDATA[lenovo]]></category><category><![CDATA[ThinkBook]]></category><category><![CDATA[ThinkPad]]></category><category><![CDATA[ThinkVision]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089572</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>每年的 MWC，一眾廠商都會相繼推出上半年的重點新機，Lenovo 亦不例外，繼 CES 後，在今年的 MWC [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>每年的 MWC，一眾廠商都會相繼推出上半年的重點新機，Lenovo 亦不例外，繼 CES 後，在今年的 MWC 亦推出了一系列的新機，當中最吸引的也有數部，現在就為大家分享一下吧。</p><h2>ThinkPad X13s Gen 1：首採 ARM 架構 ThinkPad</h2><p>今次 Lenovo 推出多部新機，當中最值得留意的，肯定是 ThinkPad 旗下首部採用 ARM 架構處理器的手提電腦 X13s Gen 1。它是世上首部採用 Qualcomm Snapdraon 8cx Gen 3 這枚 64-bit ARM 架構 5nm 制程處理器的手提電腦，而且是首部 ThinkPad 支援 5G mmWave 技術（雖然香港未用到），方便用家隨時隨地都可以連接網絡工作，加上機身採用用輕薄設計，機身厚度只有 13mm，重量亦只有 1.06kg，十分適合需要經常外攜及隨時上網工作的商務用家使用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-1280x723.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-768x434.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-1536x867.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005-2048x1156.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_005.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089577" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-1280x719.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-2048x1151.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_004-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-1280x723.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-768x434.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-1536x868.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006-2048x1157.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_006.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於其他規格，包括：內建了最高 32GB LPDDR4x 記憶體、最多 1TB PCIe SSD、13.3 吋 16：10 長闊比 1920 x 1200 解像度 IPS 熒幕及 500 萬像素 RGB 前鏡頭。Lenovo 表示將會在今年五月推出 ThinkPad X13s Gen 1，定價為 1,399 歐羅（約 HK$11,905）起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-615x580.jpg" alt="" width="615" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-615x580.jpg 615w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-955x900.jpg 955w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001-768x724.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_001.jpg 1528w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 615px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089580" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-614x580.jpg" alt="" width="614" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-614x580.jpg 614w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-953x900.jpg 953w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002-768x725.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/x13s_002.jpg 1525w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 614px" /></a></p><h2>IdeaPad Gaming 3 / 3i：入門版迷人白電競機</h2><p>去到今時今日，已不是喜歡打機的用家才會入手電競款手提電腦，一些家居環境較細，又想擁有一部具備一定效能電腦的用家，也會對入門級的電競機款有興趣。Lenovo 在今次的 MWC 就發佈了入門級的電競筆電 IdeaPad Gaming 3 / 3i（3 為 AMD 版本，3i 為 Intel 版本），設有 15 吋及 16 吋熒幕款式供用家選擇，當中尤以 15 吋機款最為吸引，因為它有白色機款，即使女性用家亦十分適合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Front_Facing_Right.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089581" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/14_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Back_Ports_Detail.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>機身設計上十分具時尚感，而且配備了最新的 Intel Core 或 AMD Ryzen 處理器，獨顯最高更可配置 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060，加上十分足夠的端子，是 Desktop Replacement 的最佳選擇之一。熒幕方面，不但具備 2560 x 1440 解像度，而且更支援最高 165Hz 更新率，即使用來打機畫面亦十分流暢。此外，它亦內建了四散熱風扇設計，打機時可以有效將機內熱力帶出機外，令系統長保穩定。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Right_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089585" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/12_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_Top_View.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>至於推出日期方面，IdeaPad Gaming 3 / 3i 的 15 吋版本，將會分別在今年的六月及五月推出，定價均為 999 歐羅（約 HK$8,503）起；至於 Gaming 3 / 3i 的 16 吋版本，則會分別在今年的七月及六月正式推出，定價均為 1,099 歐羅（約 HK$9,360）起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089584" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_IdeaPad_Gaming_3_Gen7_A_D_Cover.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2>ThinkBook 13x Gen 4 i / 14s Yoga Gen 2：設計更輕更硬淨</h2><p>另一個今年 Lenovo 新推出的機款系列就是 ThinkBook，在今次 MWC 他們推出了傳統筆電設計商務機款 ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i，以及擁有可旋轉式觸控熒幕，可作筆電可作平板二用的 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2。兩部機均採用了近年 ThinkBook 沿用的兩截深淺色機身設計，今代更採用了全金屬機身，更加硬淨之餘看上去亦更有型。另外，兩部機的機身相比上代都輕薄了，ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i 厚度及重量只有 14.9mm 及 1.26kg，而 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2 亦分別只有 16.9mm 及 1.5kg，外攜使用亦十分方便。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_13s_Gen_4_Light_Weight-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089587" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Right_Side_Ports.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>熒幕方面，ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i 採用了 13.3 吋 2.5K 幼邊框熒幕，而 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2 就採用了 14 吋 1080p 幼邊框觸控熒幕，兩部機預設設定分別只是後者支援觸控功能而前者就不支援。另外作為輕薄機款，兩部機除了都擁有 2 個支援 Thunderbolt 4 的 USB-C 插槽外，亦設有傳統的 USB-A 插槽，接駁周邊十分方便。規格方面，兩部機均內建了最新第 12 代 Intel Core i7 處理器、最高 32GB（13s）/ 40GB（14s Yoga）記憶體、Intel Iris Xe 圖像處理晶片等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089588" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/01_ThinkBook_13s_Gen4_Hero_Front_Facing_JD.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>至於推出日期方面，兩部機均會在今年六月推出發售，定價方面，ThinkBook 13s Gen 4 i 為 749 歐羅（約 HK$6,366）起，而 ThinkBook 14s Yoga Gen 2 則為 899 歐羅（約 HK$7,641）起。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1089590 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ThinkBook-14s-yoga-Lifestyle-Tent-Mode-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089591" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/08_ThinkBook_14s_Yoga_Gen2_Hero_Tent.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1089592 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_Thinkbook_14s_Yoga_Hero_Logo_Display.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2>ThinkVision M14d：解像度更高設計未變</h2><p>近年不少人都需要 WFH，如果想提升工作效率，使用雙熒幕或許也是個好選擇。今次筆者最後一項覺得值得為大家介紹的，就是 Lenovo 今次發佈的升級版便攜式外置顯示器 ThinkVision M14d。在外型上它與前代分別不大，功能上亦未有大變，不過今代熒幕解像度就提升至 2240 x 1400 2.2K，更高的解像度可說是針對近年開始 2K 解像度 16：10 長闊比熒幕變主流的商務筆電而設。當然，針對仍然在用 16：9 長闊比熒幕的用家，它亦設有按鍵可以轉換長闊比，十分體貼。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/05_ThinkVision_M14d_Hero_Front_Facing_Right.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/02_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Rear_Forward_Facing.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>至於推出日期方面，ThinkVision M14d 將會在今年八月正式推出，定價方面為 359 歐羅（約 HK$3,051）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089597" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/03_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Right_Side_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1089599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/04_ThinkVision_M14d_Tour_Left_Side_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
